# Performance & Accessibility — web_app

## Performance
- Code-split routes and heavy components
- Dynamic import for non-critical UI; prefetch on hover/visible
- Optimize images (WebP), define sizes, lazy-load
- Memoization: useMemo/useCallback only for heavy computations
- Avoid unnecessary effects and re-renders; derive state from props

## Accessibility
- Semantic HTML; ARIA only when necessary
- Contrast and focus states; keyboard navigation
- Labels for inputs; associate errors with fields
- Prefer native elements; manage roles responsibly